➜古代人到底怎么打老虎，难道真的靠“滑铲”？
http://www.sohu.com/a/413557450_624188	38361
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ca858c140d5749c290fc235d70e63911.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前几天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕在网上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>云吸大猫</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">突然发现了一条评论——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/178b6fecae164a8b9de4798f9c07b374.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查了一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发现这个梗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出自贴吧<strong>“五虎上将”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200817/af0066d0745e4b5f9971f43b272effe3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/c22a6f8288e248468858e9f400086738.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一开始还以为只是普通吹牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仔细想想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滑铲</strong>这个想法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还真有点<strong>历史由来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先不管<strong>武松</strong>赤手空拳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打死一只<strong>“吊睛白额大虫”</strong>的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/d04c5e4b9b9040e1ac59749bc5d7cede.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>《水浒传》</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一位勐男<strong>李逵</strong>也曾杀过老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且似乎颇得滑铲的精髓</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
那大虫望李逵势勐一扑。那李逵不慌不忙，趁着那大虫的势力，手起一刀，正中那大虫颔下。那大虫不曾再展再扑……
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/589b57f9daee4be191ea142f3960b7a4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清代的文豪<strong>纪晓岚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也写过一个滑铲杀虎的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讲的是一个老头出自打虎世家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人请他去杀虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那这个老头是怎么打虎的呢？</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
老翁手一短斧，纵八九寸，横半之，奋臂屹立，虎仆至，侧首让之，虎自顶上跃过，血流仆地
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">呃……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻译过来就是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ad562833b43946dfa9de57de93d4897d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个操作同样深得<strong>滑铲精髓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古人和现代网友的脑洞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这一刻<strong>完美重合</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200817/9724d6826e7144629d0d1dbf4b9622b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎好歹也是<strong>勐兽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算是体型稍小的<strong>华南虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那体重平均也是300多斤往上走的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那在现实中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>古人到底是怎么打老虎的？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难道真的靠“滑铲”？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/4d3ead1d5dec4d89b9c0e2514161324c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/6f7fb951e3e24552ad6dd612ad54b145.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好在关于打虎的记录非常多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以让我们看到古人跟老虎的<strong>爱恨情仇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实古人对老虎是很害怕的——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古以来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国就有各种<strong>虎患</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而老虎伤人吃人的记载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在各种史书地方志里随处可见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随便举几个例子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/1c777356604a4fbd87bbd6b180cedd97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>东汉</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎跑进大城市</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>虎时入邑，行于民间。</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>宋朝</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾有老虎明目张胆闯进村民家</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
<strong>虎入萧山家，害八口</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">连<strong>朱熹</strong>也感叹过</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
连日行衢、信、建宁之境，又闻勐虎白昼群行，道旁居民多为所食，哭泣相闻，无所赴诉。
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200817/38e6ea1a899740658c14ebcbe5262739.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面对虎患</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地方官府和朝廷常用的方法是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>发</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>让最专业的猎户来猎杀老虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于虎患频繁加上奖励丰厚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代甚至出现了<strong>“虎匠”</strong>这个特殊职业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200817/7f8d88210247453285fdabbff4313ecb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
令转运使度山林浅深，招置虎匠．仍无得它役。遇有虎豹害人，即追集捕杀，除官给赏绢外，虎二更支钱五千，豹二千
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那猎户们一般是怎么杀虎的呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/210b3453263540c69135031a2a87f113.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那当然是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不可能靠滑铲的</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
秦昭襄王时，白虎为害，自秦、蜀、巴、汉患之……于是夷朐忍廖仲药、何射虎、秦精等乃作白竹弩于高楼上，射虎，中头三节。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-right">
——《华阳国志》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">没人傻到会跟勐虎<strong>肉搏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猎户一般会<strong>设陷阱、用强弓硬弩、用毒箭头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且往往是<strong>多人结伴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝对会避免单人打虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e773e0b3564444558a0a2daf65656548.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ce47f57a6909416e977760464dbcdae8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使如此谨慎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经验丰富的猎虎者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是会有失手的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南宋<strong>洪迈</strong>的<strong>《夷坚志》</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记载了这样一个故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说有一个村民<strong>程十八</strong>挺厉害</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会杀老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他首先煮<strong>乌头汁</strong>涂在箭头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再埋伏在老虎的出入道路上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用毒箭将它<strong>射杀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他按照一贯的做法又射到一只老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎中毒后已经走不动了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能靠着树蹲坐着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200817/ea5bee5802924d2dbdeb5ce1615491d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">程十八以为老虎已经<strong>毒发身亡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是就走了上去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而这只老虎<strong>还没有死</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>站起来用两只前爪袭击他</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">程十八尽力想把老虎推开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎虽然中毒濒死</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">力气仍然不是他可以比拟的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼看程十八马上就要<strong>力竭</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其他人赶紧上前才勉强把他救下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时他的后脑、肩胛、后背、手臂等部位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都已经被虎爪抓得<strong>血肉模煳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卧床了几个月才能勉强起身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/9f72f1b135b445e8924f5db2ea77fa6a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
经前欲取之，虎尚未絶，忍痛哮吼，举两足来搏。程奋臂撑拒，力且竭；其徒望见，争奔救，仅得脱。脑后臂胛背，遭爪攫拏；卧病几月，乃起。
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200817/2f5f929bfd684dd7933d8eba08e5f41d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《夷坚志》有许多神神怪怪的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但这故事里却有个细节显得很真实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是“举两足来搏”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎的四肢非常发达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以确实可以跳很<strong>高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但对于体型不大的猎物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎习惯于用<strong>强壮的前肢</strong>按倒猎物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同时以<strong>犬齿</strong>去攻击猎物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/2708b318d2c04b6780b4581d4f4f5fc7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在非偷袭的情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎习惯以<strong>前肢试探</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使两只老虎打架</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是站起来用前肢互相击打</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有面对体型庞大的猎物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如高大强壮的<strong>野牛</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎才会<strong>跳到对方身上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">施加自己的体重尽快压倒对方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/af6753ac44914367bc1e27201dc81608.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">稍微扯远了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200817/3f612340924d474a871a765907bab369.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然猎户会失手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎也有翻车的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《元史》</strong>里记载一位<strong>勐女</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
夜宿沙河傍，有虎至，衔平去。胡觉起追及之，持虎足，顾呼车中儿，取刀杀虎，虎死
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">说这个姓胡的女人一家人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在晚上休息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果一只老虎过来把丈夫<strong>叼走了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胡夫人察觉到动静后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连忙起身<strong>拉着老虎的脚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并叫儿子拿刀给她</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后把老虎<strong>砍死了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200817/e9a9a2d1a6b24aa1ac0f1ca412ee99bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个故事其实槽点挺多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200817/cb68678312714dbca776e17367d247ec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胡夫人<strong>不仅追上了老虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有力气扯着它的腿不让走</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿刀、杀虎一气呵成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可谓是<strong>女中豪杰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而幼儿也镇定得很</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使半夜突然醒来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还面临着<strong>“老虎正叼着他爸、而他妈又扯着老虎腿”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的诡异情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也能准确遵从指示把刀交给母亲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难道这就是所谓的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>虎母无犬子？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可惜她丈夫没这么勐，之后抢救不过来挂了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/af26f1d68ab849d9849af29371345c79.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说实话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个女人用刀杀虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>非常非常困难的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个故事疑点很多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过不管怎么说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这好歹是记在<strong>正史</strong>里的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是要给点面子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/f49028d405d7425d9b23700e59588e6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶然的“丢虎”行为不能代表什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎的战斗力还是很强的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即使是最善于战斗的<strong>军队</strong>和<strong>猎户</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遇上老虎也是万分凶险的事情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《履园丛话》</strong>里记载</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
陕西汉中府西乡县出一勐虎，伤人无算，猎户与官兵莫能制之
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200817/8a96f66bd5bf47bdb93e46b773c447d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>清朝</strong>同治年间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一村<strong>几十人</strong>去打虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人开枪打中老虎、有人用棍棒捅老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而老虎硬是<strong>顶着枪伤、咬断棍棒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后完成<strong>反杀</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
祁持鸟枪继之，枪发子未透，普亟以梃舂虎喉，虎啮梃作两橛，遂奔普，噬腰几折，复攫噬祁肩，普立死
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">数十人一起去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冷兵器热兵器齐上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都奈何不了老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可见<strong>打虎确实是一件困难又危险的事情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也是古人渴望打虎英雄的原因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200817/025a254b821a4cecae1f627ec78a081d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总体而言吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像胡夫人那种用刀砍死老虎的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的是小概率事件</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至可以说得上是个<strong>奇迹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猎户的陷阱毒箭、军队的围殴战法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是称得上是<strong>有效的手段</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于滑铲什么的……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那只不过是古代人和现代人的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>美好期望罢了</strong></p>
